pkgmetadata.longdescription: Semiparametric Competing Risks Regression under Interval Censoring // Semiparametric regression models for the cumulative incidence function with interval-censored competing risks data as described in Bakoyannis, Yu, Yiannoutsos (2017) doi:10.1002/sim.7350. The main function fits the proportional subdistribution hazards model (Fine-Gray model), the proportional odds model, and other models that belong to the class of semiparametric generalized odds rate transformation models.
